<p itemprop="description">The head of service desk management provides strategic leadership for all user support activities across the organisation. They establish enterprise-wide service desk frameworks and ensure exceptional user experiences across all IT services.</p>

<section class="role-details">
    <h2>Typical responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Provide strategic leadership for service desk operations across the organisation</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Establish enterprise-wide service desk frameworks and governance</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Drive digital transformation of user support capabilities</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Lead user experience strategy and customer satisfaction initiatives</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Represent user support interests in executive forums</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Ensure alignment with accessibility and inclusion requirements</li>
        <li itemprop="responsibility">Develop strategic partnerships for user support innovation</li>
    </ul>
</section>

